Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:07.50,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,348)}我到底在保護什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.92,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}不畏失去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.63,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}即便長大成人 也心懷夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.63,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}因為我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.13,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}自己能將這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.05,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,351)}視為驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.10,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}吐出來 捨棄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.98,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}見到你
